msgid "**MaxFrame SDK version**"
msgstr "**MaxFrame SDK 版本**"

msgid "Use MaxFrame SDK **2.7.0** or above (``pip install maxframe>=2.7.0``)."
msgstr ""
"请使用 MaxFrame SDK **2.7.0** 及以上版本（``pip install maxframe>=2.7.0``"
"）。"

msgid "#"
msgstr ""

msgid "**Audio uploaded to OSS**"
msgstr "**上传音频至 OSS**"

msgid ""
"**Built-in distributed audio operators** for decode, metadata, language "
"detection, transcription, and VAD."
msgstr "**内置分布式音频算子**：支持 decode、元信息、语言检测、转写与 VAD。"

msgid "**DPE enabled**"
msgstr "**开通 DPE 引擎**"

msgid ""
"**Direct OSS ingestion** with ``.url.download()`` and no object table "
"dependency."
msgstr ""
"**URL 直通 OSS 音频**：通过 ``.url.download()`` 直接处理 OSS 音频，无需"
"依赖 Object Table。"

msgid ""
"**Flexible resource control** for CPU/GPU style workloads through "
"operator and engine parameters."
msgstr "**灵活的资源控制**：可通过算子与引擎参数适配 CPU/GPU 风格负载。"

msgid ""
"**Low operational overhead** by reusing MaxCompute elastic compute and "
"storage stack."
msgstr "**低运维成本**：复用 MaxCompute 弹性计算与存储体系。"

msgid "**MaxCompute enabled**"
msgstr "**开通 MaxCompute**"

msgid "**OSS RAM role authorization**"
msgstr "**OSS RAM 角色授权**"

msgid ""
"**Speech transcription** for podcasts, courses, interviews, and meeting "
"recordings."
msgstr ""
"**语音内容转录**：适用于播客、课程录音、访谈、会议音频等内容的批量转写，"
"便于后续归档、检索和内容消费。"

msgid ""
"**Structured processing** for customer service calls and business "
"recordings."
msgstr ""
"**业务录音结构化处理**：适用于客服录音、服务通话、业务访谈等场景，将非"
"结构化音频内容转化为可分析的文本数据。"

msgid ""
"**Subtitle generation** and text extraction from audio tracks in media "
"files."
msgstr ""
"**字幕生成与文本提取**：适用于对音视频中的音轨进行识别，生成字幕文本或"
"提取语音内容。"

msgid ""
"**Training data preparation** for speech recognition and speech "
"understanding models."
msgstr ""
"**训练数据准备**：适用于从原始音频中批量提取文本，为语音识别、语音理解等"
"模型训练准备基础语料。"

