msgstr "MaxCompute 参数占位："

msgid "MaxFrame Multimodal Audio Operator Practice"
msgstr "MaxFrame 多模态音视频算子开发实践"

msgid "OSS placeholders:"
msgstr "OSS 参数占位："

msgid "Pipeline"
msgstr "核心流程说明"

msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr "前提条件"

msgid "Requirement"
msgstr "条件"

msgid "Source audio files are available in a target OSS bucket."
msgstr "原始音频文件已上传至目标 OSS Bucket。"

msgid "Technical highlights"
msgstr "核心技术亮点"

msgid ""
"The role has OSS read permission (for example "
"``AliyunOSSReadOnlyAccess``)."
msgstr "该角色具备 OSS 读权限（例如 ``AliyunOSSReadOnlyAccess``）。"

msgid "The role trust policy allows MaxCompute service to assume the role."
msgstr "该角色的信任策略允许 MaxCompute 服务扮演该角色。"

msgid ""
"Use ``.audio`` operators for decode, language detection, transcription, "
"and VAD:"
msgstr "使用 ``.audio`` 算子进行解码、语言检测、语音转写与 VAD："

msgid "Use cases"
msgstr "适用场景"

#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"When using ``.url.download(storage_options={\"role_arn\": ...})``, "
"MaxFrame reads OSS data by assuming a RAM role. Make sure:"
msgstr ""
"使用 ``.url.download(storage_options={\"role_arn\": ...})`` 时，MaxFrame "
"会通过 RAM 角色读取 OSS 数据。请确保："

msgid ""
"With MaxCompute + MaxFrame, you can run a unified distributed pipeline "
"from OSS audio ingestion to structured transcription output. This "
"tutorial focuses on practical audio processing with built-in MaxFrame "
"``.audio`` operators."
msgstr ""
"MaxCompute 提供 Data+AI 一体化能力，通过分布式计算框架 MaxFrame，支持对"
"音频数据进行统一调度与批量处理。用户可以基于 MaxFrame 构建从音频下载到"
"语音识别的完整处理链路，对海量原始音频进行自动化转写，并将识别结果输出为"
"结构化数据，便于后续分析、检索和模型训练使用。"

msgid "``.url.download()`` and ``.audio.*`` operators run on DPE."
msgstr "``.url.download()`` 与 ``.audio.*`` 算子在 DPE 上执行。"

msgid "Troubleshooting"
msgstr "常见问题排查"

msgid "OSS access denied"
msgstr "OSS 访问被拒绝"

msgid ""
"**Symptom**: ``.url.download(storage_options={\"role_arn\": ...})`` fails"
" with an access denied error."
msgstr ""
"**现象**：调用 ``.url.download(storage_options={\"role_arn\": ...})`` 时报访"
"问被拒绝错误。"

msgid "**Cause**: Wrong or missing role permissions."
msgstr "**原因**：角色权限配置错误或缺失。"

msgid "**Solution**: Verify the following:"
msgstr "**解决方案**：请逐一确认以下事项："

msgid ""
"**Role ARN is correct** — double-check the ``role_arn`` value in "
"``storage_options`` matches the RAM role configured in the Alibaba Cloud "
"console."
msgstr ""
"**Role ARN 正确** — 确认 ``storage_options`` 中的 ``role_arn`` 值与阿里"
"云控制台配置的 RAM 角色一致。"

msgid ""
"**OSS read permission** — ensure the RAM role has the "
"``AliyunOSSReadOnlyAccess`` policy (or equivalent custom policy) "
"attached, granting ``oss:GetObject`` permission on the target bucket."
msgstr ""
"**OSS 读权限** — 确认 RAM 角色已附加 ``AliyunOSSReadOnlyAccess`` 策略"
"（或等效自定义策略），具备目标 Bucket 的 ``oss:GetObject`` 权限。"

